Wildcard .* matches any character any number of times including zero

[Terms aggregation](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-aggregations-bucket-terms-aggregation.html) will give you unique &quot;ids&quot; and number of docs under them.

